r7370 | zorglub | 2004-04-18 20:21:09 +0200 (Sun, 18 Apr 2004) | 22 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/Makefile.am
   M /trunk/NEWS
   M /trunk/include/network.h
   M /trunk/include/stream_output.h
   M /trunk/include/vlc/vlc.h
